Revision history for Miril

0.008   13/09/2010
        * Comprehensive code refactoring
		* New data file format
		* New list API for flexible list publishing
		* Form validatation
		* PSGI support
		* Bundled standalone server
		* Command line publishing script
		* Better exception handling
		* Updated documentation

0.007   26/11/2009
        * Miscellaneous bug fixes

0.006   26/11/2009
        * Added files missing from MANIFEST

0.005   25/11/2009
        * A lot of refactoring
		* Added Miril::Hacking for developers

0.004   05/10/2009
        * Added support for Text::Template
		* Added support for topics (categories)

0.003   25/09/2009
        * Fixed small bug in Miril::Model::File::XMLTPP.

0.002   24/09/2009
        * POD fixes.

0.001   23/09/2009
        * First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
